                        We are engaged in a passionate journey to establish ourselves as the lowest-cost, high-quality healthcare service provider in the world. At Rajendra, we are convinced that ‘quality’ and ‘lowest cost’ are not mutually exclusive when it comes to healthcare delivery. In fact, we are well on our way to demonstrating that we are not running our institutions as just another number-only business, but we are attractively placed to create an affordable, globally-benchmarked quality-driven healthcare services model.
                        Rajendra Hospital at Ashokapuram near the Christian college was inscribed in the history book of Kozhikode ever since 1940. It has begun its services from a car shed when there were only a handful of doctors in the city of Kozhikode. Now, the hospital stands tall and high on the same soil of its emergence at the heart of the city.
                        .
