                <div class="col-sm-8 wrapper-italic pt-3">
                    <p>Located in the heart of Calicut city, and one of the oldest hospitals in the region, the hospital was established in 1940 by Late Dr P. Balram. From its early years, the hospital and its doctors focused on providing access to medical care to the common man, placing service to the poor of utmost importance. His sons, Late Dr P. Rajendran, Late Dr P Mohanraj and Late Dr P. Ramesh Kumar continued the tradition. The Hospital always stay as an integral part of Calicut City.</p>
                        </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4 wrapper-old">
                    <img class="dep" src="./img/founder.jpg">
                    <p> <b>
                        “Managing a hospital should not be considered a way to make money”. One should provide scientific and good treatment. Rajendra Hospital should always remain one for the common man”.
                        -Dr P Balram.</b>
</p>
